<br>
This is a bad design decision in a game of epic fantasy, where everyone is striving to be heroic.  The balance under level 20 seems so much nicer.<br>
<br>
In order to force grouping in the game with less powerful NPCs, however, it would be necessary to put in several more NPCs with less experience awarded.  More NPCs = heavier server load.  Therefore, fewer, more powerful critters grace the surface (and depths) of Norrath.<br>
<br>
A byproduct of this is that pet classes, who utilize NPCs, control only one hefty pet, rather than a few smaller pets.<br>
<br>
The end result of this is the epic feel of the game is greatly watered down.  Capabilities of PCs are overshadowed by those of NPCs of lower level.  Everyone notices it.  Everyone (it seems) is bothered by it.  There is no fix for it that wouldn't fundamentally re-balance EQ.<br>
<br>
Hopefully the next game to come along doesn't have this issue. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilismeleetalk.showMessage?topicID=101.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilismeleetalk.showMessage?topicID=91.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilismeleetalk.threadControl?topicID=94.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilismeleetalk.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=94.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilismeleetalk.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=94.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="brellserilisfrm48">Town Crier (Rules & Announcements)<option value="brellserilisbrellserilisdiscussion">The Commons (General EQ Discussion)<option value="brellserilisfrm56">Salutations & Congratulations <option value="brellserilisfrm33">Dreams & Diversions (Off Topic)<option value="brellserilisfrm55">Fellowship of Guilds (Guildchat)<option value="brellserilisbrellslairadminonly">Brell's Lair (Admin only)<option value="brellserilisfrm64">Archived Threads<option value="brellserilismeleetalk">Tome: Races and Classes <option value="brellserilisroleplaying">Tome: History of Norrath<option value="brellserilisfrm49">Tome: Vision